POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (11): GLOBAL ACUTE FLACCID PARALYSIS CVDPV2 (DEMOCRATIC REPUBLIC OF THE CONGO, NIGERIA), CVDPV3 (ACUTE FLACCID PARALYSIS ISRAEL), ENVIRONMENTAL SAMPLES CVDPV2 (COTE D'IVOIRE, MAURITANIA), PALESTINIAN AUTHORITY, REQUEST FOR INFORMATION
